         <string>Imports kwneuro and kwneuro_slicer_bridge, then pushes a small synthetic 3D volume through InSceneVolumeResource and verifies its array and affine round-trip correctly. A failure here means one of those three steps did not work — typically because kwneuro or the bridge is not installed, or an import failed; re-run Install / Update above or check the console for the specific error.</string>
